---
interface Props {
  city: string;
  region: string;
}

const { city, region } = Astro.props;
---

<section>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">
      Why {city} Contractors Choose Rebel Ape
    </h2>

    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 text-center">
      We work with contractors throughout {city} and {region}—not because we're the local agency on every corner, but because what we do actually works.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-12 text-rebel-green mb-3">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75V4.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.5 0V2.25A.75.75 0 0 1 12 1.5ZM5.636 4.136a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0l1.592 1.591a.75.75 0 0 1-1.061 1.06L5.636 5.197a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.061Zm12.728 0a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-1.591 1.592a.75.75 0 0 1-1.061-1.061l1.591-1.591a.75.75 0 0 1 1.061 0Zm-6.816 4.496a.75.75 0 0 1 .82.311l5.228 7.917a.75.75 0 0 1-.777 1.148l-2.097-.43 1.045 3.9a.75.75 0 0 1-1.45.388l-1.044-3.899-1.601 1.42a.75.75 0 0 1-1.247-.606l.569-9.47a.75.75 0 0 1 .554-.68ZM3 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75H6a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5H3.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 10.5Zm14.25 0a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h2.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5H18a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75Zm-8.962 3.712a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.061l-1.591 1.591a.75.75 0 1 1-1.061-1.06l1.591-1.592a.75.75 0 0 1 1.061 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center">No Contracts, No BS Guarantees</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            We don't hide behind guarantees that sound great but mean nothing. If we're not delivering results, fire us. That's how it should be. We earn our spot every month by actually getting your phone ringing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-12 text-rebel-green mb-3">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.25 6.75a3.75 3.75 0 1 1 7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1-7.5 0ZM15.75 9.75a3 3 0 1 1 6 0 3 3 0 0 1-6 0ZM2.25 9.75a3 3 0 1 1 6 0 3 3 0 0 1-6 0ZM6.31 15.117A6.745 6.745 0 0 1 12 12a6.745 6.745 0 0 1 6.709 7.498.75.75 0 0 1-.372.568A12.696 12.696 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.305 0-4.47-.612-6.337-1.684a.75.75 0 0 1-.372-.568 6.787 6.787 0 0 1 1.019-4.38Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              <path d="M5.082 14.254a8.287 8.287 0 0 0-1.308 5.135 9.687 9.687 0 0 1-1.764-.44l-.115-.04a.563.563 0 0 1-.373-.487l-.01-.121a3.75 3.75 0 0 1 3.57-4.047ZM20.226 19.389a8.287 8.287 0 0 0-1.308-5.135 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 3.57 4.047l-.01.121a.563.563 0 0 1-.373.486l-.115.04c-.567.2-1.156.349-1.764.441Z" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center">Marketing Partners, Not Vendors</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            We're not just an agency you pay to run ads. We're your marketing team. We own our results. If something's not working, we figure out why and fix it—together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-12 text-rebel-green mb-3">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 6a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h2.25a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v2.25a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H6a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V6Zm9.75 0a3 3 0 0 1 3-3H18a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v2.25a3 3 0 0 1-3 3h-2.25a3 3 0 0 1-3-3V6ZM3 15.75a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h2.25a3 3 0 0 1 3 3V18a3 3 0 0 1-3 3H6a3 3 0 0 1-3-3v-2.25Zm9.75 0a3 3 0 0 1 3-3H18a3 3 0 0 1 3 3V18a3 3 0 0 1-3 3h-2.25a3 3 0 0 1-3-3v-2.25Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center">Complete Systems, Not Random Tactics</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            A website alone doesn't work. Ads alone don't work. SEO alone doesn't work. We build complete lead generation systems where everything works together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-4">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-12 text-rebel-green mb-3">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.25 13.5a8.25 8.25 0 0 1 8.25-8.25.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v6.75H18a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75 8.25 8.25 0 0 1-16.5 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.75 3a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75 8.25 8.25 0 0 1 8.25 8.25.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75h-7.5a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75V3Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center">Results Over Promises</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            We don't promise market domination on a tiny budget. We work within your constraints, get the best possible results, and show you exactly what's working through tracking and reporting.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
